thread.title: MARIE FRANCE
thread.title_full: Redspot Car Rentals reviewed by MARIE FRANCE

author: MARIE FRANCE
title: MARIE FRANCE
text: We have rent a intermediate car for 3 days. The car was pretty good very comfortable and easy to drive. Unfortunately when we brought back there was no more place in the park and we didn't know how to manage it. A small sign on the box where you have to drop the key said that we can park the car in another level. Even with this problem I recommend !
